Package software.kes.kraftwerk.constraints

Class LocalTimeRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.kes.kraftwerk.constraints.LocalTimeRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint<java.time.LocalTime>
    public final class LocalTimeRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements Constraint<java.time.LocalTime>
    A range of LocalTimes. Like all ranges, it is immutable and its span always includes a minimum of one value.

    Construct using one of the static methods (inclusive(java.time.LocalTime, java.time.LocalTime), exclusive(java.time.LocalTime, java.time.LocalTime)),

    or by using from(java.time.LocalTime): 

     LocalTimeRange.from(LocalTime.of(0, 0)).to(LocalTime.of(12, 0))      // inclusive upper bound
 LocalTimeRange.from(LocalTime.of(0, 0)).until(LocalTime.of(12, 0))   // exclusive upper bound
